[25/10/2017 05:27:57] <font color="#0000ff">con tus encantos,</font>
[25/10/2017 05:28:03] <font color="#0000ff">y llevamos media vida</font>
[25/10/2017 05:28:03] <font color="#0000ff">recordando aquel temblor.</font>
