[25/10/2017 11:19:39] <font color="#00ff00">Verás...</font>
[25/10/2017 11:19:39] <font color="#ffffff">- No, Kitty. Robert tiene razón.</font>
[25/10/2017 11:19:42] <font color="#00ff00">No te preocupes,</font>
